                                    <p class="o_mail_no_margin o_default_snippet_text">We need you to update your account information. If there is ever a problem with your account, this information will make it easier for you to log back in.</p>
                                    <div class="text-center" style="margin-top:15px;">
                                        <a href="#" class="o_mail_link o_default_snippet_text">Read More...</a>
